Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
metric_current_run_id(25.10)                      metric_current_run_id(25.10)

Name
       metric_current_run_id

Syntax
        metric_current_run_id

       Default: The default value of this string variable is not set.

       Provides  the  current  unique  run  ID returned by the advanced metric
       server.

       It contains the identifier used with the advanced metric server so that
       multiple uploads of the data (such as, data upload after  fplan,  after
       prects,  after  cts)  are  seen as a single execution of the tools. The
       identifier is created by the advanced  metric  server  so  that  it  is
       unique and is stored in metric_current_run_id.

